          <text id="/covid_education/corona_precautions/congratulate_client:label">
            <value>Mpongeze mama/mlezi, vizuri, ni vyema kuendelea kuchukua tahadhari juu ya Ugonjwa wa Corona, pia amjuilishe mlengwa ugonjwa huo bado upo na unaendelea kuathiri nchi nyingi ikiwemo nchi yetu na nchi jirani.</value>
          </text>
